\ddot{y}_{1}\\
\ddot{y}_{2}
\end{array}\right)=\underbrace{\left(\begin{array}{cc}
\sin x_{3} & \phantom{-}x_{4}\cos x_{3}\\
\cos x_{3} & -x_{4}\sin x_{3}
